<?php include "../header/header.php"; ?><html><body><div class="container"><br><h1>Convert String To Int in Unity</h1><br><br>A couple of methods to convert string to integer: <br><br>1. int.Parse() :<br>	Ex: String s="9";<br>		int x = int.Parse(s);<br><br>2. Convert.ToInt32()<br>	Ex:  int value = Convert.ToInt32(999);<br><br><br>Bonus: Convert a Button Value to Integer in C#<br><br><code><br>	Ex: public void OverSelect(Button b)<br>    	{<br>       		oversFinal = int.Parse(b.GetComponentInChildren<Text>().text);<br>    	}<br></code><br>    -> Attach the same button to the button parameter list in the <i>onClick()</i> function.</div></body></html><br><br><?php include "../footer/footer.php"; ?>